OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1776449465
OL,3,CWarning care homes may have to turn
OL,4,Cpeople away due to staffing strain
OL,6,FThose in the care sector are warning
OL,7,Fthat homes may be forced to turn away
OL,8,Felderly people with dementia following
OL,9,Fpressures in recruiting overseas staff.
OL,11,FCare Forum Wales (CFW) have raised
OL,12,Fconcerns that tighter immigration
OL,13,Frules are impacting a key area of care
OL,14,Fhome staff.
OL,16,FNavjit Kaur is the registered manager
OL,17,Fof Springbank care home in Barry and
OL,18,Fshe said without overseas staff, she
OL,19,Fdoes not think the home "would be able
OL,20,Fto manage anything at all".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
