OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1776449465
OL,3,CWarning care homes may have to turn
OL,4,Cpeople away due to staffing strain
OL,6,FThroughout the pandemic, Navjit
OL,7,Fstruggled to retain staff, with
OL,8,Fworkers from overseas helping to
OL,9,Fmanage the workload. She said: "The
OL,10,Flocal staff resigned, we were
OL,11,Fstruggling, we were working on half
OL,12,Fthe staff number.
OL,14,F"It was impossible to provide the
OL,15,Flevel of care that the residents
OL,16,Fdeserved."
OL,18,FNavjit said she employs 80 staff
OL,19,Fmembers in total, of which 57 are
OL,20,Foverseas staff.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
