PN,46203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1776449465
OL,3,CWarning care homes may have to turn
OL,4,Cpeople away due to staffing strain
OL,6,FNurse assistant Salomi, who works in
OL,7,FSpringbank and is from India, said
OL,8,Fthat she cannot bring her family to
OL,9,Fthis country, which impacts her mental
OL,10,Fhealth.
OL,12,FShe explained: "It's really difficult
OL,13,Ffor me to bring my husband over here
OL,14,Fand I think it will be good for me if
OL,15,Fthe government changed the rules to
OL,16,Fbring dependents with us here.
OL,18,F"We are giving our 100% to this
OL,19,Fcountry, with full dedication and full
OL,20,Fpotential."
OL,26,@tD@POUzD@AOU|D@KO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/11
