PN,46204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1776449465
OL,3,CWarning care homes may have to turn
OL,4,Cpeople away due to staffing strain
OL,6,FThea Brain, Policy Advisor at Care
OL,7,FForum Wales said there are "two quite
OL,8,Fpernicious myths being peddled around
OL,9,Fthis idea that preferential treatment
OL,10,Fis given to migrant labour, because
OL,11,Fit's cheaper".
OL,13,FShe added: "The idea that migrant
OL,14,Flabour is cheaper and more convenient
OL,15,Fis a myth."
OL,17,F"There's quite poisonous rhetoric and
OL,18,Fa climate of real fear, around people
OL,19,Fcoming into the country and these
OL,20,Fpeople are coming legally."
OL,26,@uD@LOUyD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1776449465
OL,3,CWarning care homes may have to turn
OL,4,Cpeople away due to staffing strain
OL,6,FMs Brain raised concerns that there
OL,7,Fare other countries that would take
OL,8,Fthe workers' "valuable skills and
OL,9,Flabour".
OL,11,FMario Kreft MBE, the Chair of CFW,
OL,12,Fwarned the consequences for not taking
OL,13,Fany action could be "potentially
OL,14,Fhorrendous".
OL,16,F"If care homes and domiciliary care
OL,17,Fcompanies don't have enough staff,
OL,18,Fthey will either have to reduce the
OL,19,Fnumber of people for whom they provide
OL,20,Fcare or shut down completely," he
OL,21,Fclaimed.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
