OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1776449465
OL,3,CWarning care homes may have to turn
OL,4,Cpeople away due to staffing strain
OL,6,F"Things are bad enough now but even
OL,7,Fmore people won't be able to get into
OL,8,Fhospital when they need to and down
OL,9,Fthe line it's something that could
OL,10,Fcost lives."
OL,12,FIn its election manifesto, CFW is
OL,13,Furging the next Welsh Government to
OL,14,Ffollow Scotland's lead in sponsoring
OL,15,Foverseas care workers.
OL,17,FThe Scottish Government provides
OL,18,F#500,000 to support international
OL,19,Fsocial care workers who are already in
OL,20,Fthe UK displaced by visa changes, to
OL,21,Fsettle and work in Scotland.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/11
