CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1776449465
OL,3,CWarning care homes may have to turn
OL,4,Cpeople away due to staffing strain
OL,6,FCFW said international recruitment is
OL,7,Fno longer optional but essential to
OL,8,Fkeep care home services running.
OL,10,FA spokesperson for Plaid Cymru said:
OL,11,F"A Plaid Cymru government would
OL,12,Fchampion the creation of a Wales-
OL,13,Fspecific visa system and shortage
OL,14,Foccupation list to ensure that our
OL,15,Fpublic services are not hampered by a
OL,16,Flack of qualified staff, and that
OL,17,FWales can meet its own workforce
OL,18,Fneeds."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1776449465
OL,3,CWarning care homes may have to turn
OL,4,Cpeople away due to staffing strain
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Welsh Conservative
OL,7,Fsaid: "Social care is under
OL,8,Fsignificant pressure after 27 years of
OL,9,Fpoor workforce planning by Labour,
OL,10,Fpropped up by Plaid Cymru, and it is
OL,11,Fdeeply concerning to hear warnings
OL,12,Fabout potential service reductions.
OL,14,FThey added: "We will take action to
OL,15,Fstrengthen social care by improving
OL,16,Fjoint working with the NHS and
OL,17,Festablishing an Independent Commission
OL,18,Fto deliver long-term, sustainable
OL,19,Ffunding solutions.
OL,26,@oD@GOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
