OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1776449465
OL,3,CWarning care homes may have to turn
OL,4,Cpeople away due to staffing strain
OL,6,F"Our plan to fix the NHS and social
OL,7,Fcare will deliver dignity for older
OL,8,Fpeople and ensure they can retain
OL,9,Ftheir independence for as long as
OL,10,Fpossible."
OL,12,FWelsh Labour said it "will ensure all
OL,13,Fcare workers have the same basic
OL,14,Frights at work by adopting the Migrant
OL,15,FCare Workers Charter, including the
OL,16,Fprovision to be a sponsor of last
OL,17,Fresort".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@JO]
