PN,46210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1776449465
OL,3,CWarning care homes may have to turn
OL,4,Cpeople away due to staffing strain
OL,6,FReform Wales said: "People are fed up
OL,7,Fof being told that unlimited
OL,8,Fimmigration is 'essential' to fill
OL,9,Fworkforce gaps.
OL,11,F"There are tens of thousands of
OL,12,Funemployed young people in Wales
OL,13,Fliving on benefits who deserve the
OL,14,Fdignity of work in key sectors. Only
OL,15,FReform UK will make work pay by ending
OL,16,Fthe welfare trap."
OL,18,FThe Green Party and the Liberal
OL,19,FDemocrats have been approached for
OL,20,Fcomment.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/11
